text: Mohammad Imran (born 25 December 1996) is a Pakistani cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Sui Northern Gas Pipelines Limited in the 2015–16 Quaid- e-Azam Trophy on 23 November 2015. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Pakistani cricketers Category:Bahawalpur cricketers Category:Faisalabad cricketers Category:Lahore Qalandars cricketers Category:Sui Northern Gas Pipelines Limited cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
